description:
Is Biden A Putin Puppet?

Dumbest Conspiracy Theory Just Got Dumber! 

Phone calls from Al Pacino, Bibi Netanyahu, Barack Obama, and Bernie Sanders!

Featuring award winning journalist Aaron Maté, Mike MacRae, Ron Placone, and Stef Zamorano!
